    <item>
      <title>Mail of the Wild - Classic Variants</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/525169</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">3d961b2732b8c955d04ec24fdb39a412a3d48eb6</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:25:15 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/668301f5d643e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6683021d02992.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66830222c2dac.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6683022a0e274.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6683023524535.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6683023e683e9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6683024bb1e68.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/668302775a66e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6683027c08cd8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6683028331f2e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66830284ea761.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Tunic of the Wild is easily my favorite Tunic in BOTW and TOTK- tbh, it's my favorite Tunic/design for [Hero Name] as a whole.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;However, when it came to it's color and dying it, it always left me with wanting &lt;i&gt;more- &lt;/i&gt;something based on the colored Tunics- Mails you could get in the classic games for more defense (or dmg in LA).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;One retexture made by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2785270"&gt;Cool Peas&lt;/a&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/457509"&gt;Better Wild Set Color&lt;/a&gt;- it essentially fixed the base green for me as it was too dull- and dying it green not only makes the shorts green, but the undershirt a yellowish/orange I'm really not a fan of... and this fixed it- &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;however it was reliant on 1.1.2 ResourceSizeTable&lt;/span&gt;... although &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;I fixed that&lt;/span&gt; by just removing it and changing the format of the .dds files to make it work on any version of the game- and I fixed a little green spot on the undershirt sleeve that was hard to see. Due to the original mod not being active, and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Cool Peas not being online for 5 months as of now&lt;/span&gt;, I am including their Default Green I fixed for those who missed out- if they ever return and request it,&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; I will gladly remove it from this.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;NOW- to the Mail Variants... at first I did the ones based on ALBW, then decided to do the ALTTP style ones... and then last minute I did LA variants. All are included so you may select which you prefer- or you can even mix and match or delete ones you dislike, and I &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;included a .txt that lists each armor texture's filename.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Finally, these all &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;should work regardless of your game version&lt;/span&gt;, although I am playing on 1.2.1... however, &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;armor icons are not changed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;But ye... that's it- I hope you all enjoy- and go show love to &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2785270"&gt;Cool Peas&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/457509"&gt;original Green recolor&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;\/ MODS FEATURED IN SCREENSHOTS \/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/453885"&gt;Invisible Batteries&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1624188"&gt;MelonSpeedruns&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/449762"&gt;Invisible Fuses&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;- by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2706240"&gt;Zenovis&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/524712"&gt;Sheath Position's Restored for Invisible Fuses&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1437551"&gt;borkiee (me :3)&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/523154"&gt;Femme Hero&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;- by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2233605"&gt;SpaceGeorge&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/448120"&gt;The Hero's Eyeliner&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2233605"&gt;SpaceGeorge&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(Recreated myself for Femme Hero)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/457025"&gt;The Hero's Nail Polish&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2233605"&gt;SpaceGeorge&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(Recreated myself for Femme Hero)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/453950"&gt;Hero's Original Arm Restored (Optional Triangle)&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;- by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1630162"&gt;Lord Bubbles&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/457509"&gt;Better Wild Set Color&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;- by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2785270"&gt;Cool Peas&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(This was broken and relied on an older version- but I fixed it and included it here)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/456211" class="SelectedElement"&gt;Hero's Weapon's Repaired&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;- by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1935258"&gt;Asalazar&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/451479"&gt;Improved Resized Royal Shields&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1763398"&gt;Bunny_Bax&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;A DualSense UI mod that I can no longer find on GB, or recall the name of the creator- the only two up are different :(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;/\ MODS FEATURED IN SCREENSHOTS /\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/mail_of_the_wild_options.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
      <category>Armor set</category>
      <category>Models</category>
