    <item>
      <title>Detailed Brown-Skinned Hero's Pride Pack</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/525030</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">12f5df6a9716f8c77667870e1cbbb119b5451289</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 07:14:14 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/668255093d1d7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66825359a0dc8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66824b6a8e820.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66824b6b48be7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6682535a1e219.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;An optional pack for my &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/472228"&gt;Detailed Brown-Skinned Hero&lt;/a&gt; project, this mod allows for multiple &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Pride Flag facepaint&lt;/span&gt; and &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Top Surgery scar&lt;/span&gt; options. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Pride Flag Face Paint Options&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pride (Rainbow)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Transgender&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bisexual&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pansexual&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Asexual&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nonbinary&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Genderfluid&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Genderqueer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Scar Options&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Top surgery scars only (styled after the Ancient Sky Civilization's geometric designs)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Nipples only&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Top surgery scars with nipples&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Top and bottom surgery scars (located on the left forearm)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bottom surgery scars only&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Top and bottom surgery scars with nipples&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod has been tested only on version 1.2.0 of TotK. However, because it contains &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;no RSTB edits&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, it is &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;compatible with all versions of the game&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Instructions for manual merging of optional customizations&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Note:&#13;
 Always keep a clean backup of your files, in case you make a mistake. I&#13;
 am not responsible for corrupted mods or save data.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Begin with your chosen optional customization, [&lt;b&gt;Optional Mod A]&lt;/b&gt;, to add to the base mod, [&lt;b&gt;Base Mod B]&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Under &lt;code&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Optional Mod A] &lt;/b&gt;&gt; romfs &gt; TexToGo&lt;/code&gt;, select the file(s) located in this subfolder. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Copy all the files selected in Step #2.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Paste all of the copied files from Step #2 into &lt;code&gt;[Base Mod B] &gt; romfs &gt; TexToGo&lt;/code&gt;. If you see a warning pop-up window with the header “Replace or Skip Files,” choose the option to &lt;code&gt;Replace the file(s) in the destination&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Congratulations, you have successfully manually merged Brown-Skinned Link with Shading, with your chosen optional customization!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Acknowledgements:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;br&gt;Many thanks to &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2745192"&gt;@MaxLastBreath&lt;/a&gt; for his &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/480138"&gt;UltraCam&lt;/a&gt; tool, which was used to take preview shots.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Other mods:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/525026"&gt;Pride Flag Face Paint &lt;/a&gt;- Various Pride Flag face paint options for the Hero (default skin tone). Happy Pride!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/523154"&gt;Femme Hero&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; - A &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;femme version of the Hero&lt;/span&gt;. Voice, cutscene audio, and pronouns included.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/449532"&gt;Top Surgery Scars&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; – &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Top surgery scars&lt;/span&gt; and more for the Hero (default skin tone).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/416493"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pride Shirts for the Hero (BotW Wii U)&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/a&gt;- Various &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Pride shirts&lt;/span&gt; for the Hero.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/448120"&gt;The Hero's Eyeliner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; – Various &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;eyeliner&lt;/span&gt; styles for the Hero.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/facepaint-rainbow_5b8c1.zip" type="application/zip"/>
