      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/668242c8e9bba.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66823de86aeb5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66823de6e8808.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6682430108f28.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66823de9c396c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66823de9b22a7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6682441d6f486.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66823de8f255e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66823de9747da.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;This mod gives our Hero multiple &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Pride Flag facepaint&lt;/span&gt; options. The following flags are available:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ol class="SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pride (Rainbow)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Transgender&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bisexual&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pansexual&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Asexual&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nonbinary&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Genderfluid&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Genderqueer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;Each mod contains a unique retexture of &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;the hero's default head&lt;/span&gt;.&#13;
 Please note that this means the user can only have one of these &#13;
lipstick mods in effect at a time, and that they are incompatible with &#13;
other mods that retexture the hero's head.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The face texture used when dyeing the Charged/Ember/Frostbite Headdresses is unaffected, to avoid visual clashing with the decorative tear-shaped ornaments on the cheeks.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Disclaimers:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;This mod has been tested only on &lt;b&gt;version 1.2.0 of TotK&lt;/b&gt;. However, because it contains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;no RSTB edits&lt;/span&gt;, it is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;compatible with all versions of the game&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Acknowledgements:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;br&gt;Many thanks to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2745192"&gt;@MaxLastBreath&lt;/a&gt; for his &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/480138"&gt;UltraCam&lt;/a&gt; tool, which was used to take preview shots.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Other mods:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/523154"&gt;Femme Hero&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; - A &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;femme version of the Hero&lt;/span&gt;. Voice, cutscene audio, and pronouns included.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/449532"&gt;Top Surgery Scars&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;–&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Top surgery scars&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and more for the Hero (default skin tone). Happy Pride!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/416493"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pride Shirts for the Hero (BotW Wii U)&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/a&gt;- Various &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Pride shirts&lt;/span&gt; for the Hero.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/472228"&gt;Detailed Brown-Skinned Hero&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;– The Hero with&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;brown skin&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and additional detailing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/448120"&gt;The Hero's 