      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/523538</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">637461ce1117e45cbe5ec191f8f14b2b01f42703</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 02:06:20 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788a62d0f8f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788ab3cb0f8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788ac2ebf04.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788adb070c9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667f51df516b4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788af4b4937.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788b05641cf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788b54a5689.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788b5ea1ec6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788b9be61bd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788bae899a7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788bcb5a004.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788bfd08047.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788c1b31b27.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667f522fd3ff7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788c6db2f94.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788c3c7717f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788c85ea838.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788c30a5a13.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788c531fea7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788c8bea40a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788cb8007bc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788cd96abd0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788ceeefaa3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667f525f8f4b5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788d036dfc0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/668210f9e5bac.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/668210fada056.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788d36d31dd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66788d454b882.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Updated Animations &amp; Bug fixes&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Added a No Fox Mask option&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Improvement&lt;/em&gt;: Redid the Left/Right/Up/Down Animations for making it look way more dynamic&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Stealth Mask didnt have physics&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Big Mask with deity eyes addon had eye clipping&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Hands on Hip addon had Problems&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This armor belonged to a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Guardian&lt;/span&gt; created by the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Goddess&lt;/span&gt; to aid the one owning the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Triforce of courage&lt;/span&gt; at the Time, the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Ancient Hero&lt;/span&gt;. After its creation, the Guardian mostly lived with the Sheikah because it possessed immense strength from the Goddess, but it lacked in combat skills, and it liked Naruto. To address this, it trained with the Sheikah.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Guardian also assisted all races whenever they needed help, believing it to be their purpose. It lived through countless adventures with the Ancient Hero. However, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;no one really knew who they were&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Standalone Armor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; for Link, sold at the &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Bargainer statue&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; only at &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Lookout landing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Support All Versions Besides &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;1.0.0&lt;/span&gt; (Gamebanana Rule)&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;(Mod Mergers + Tkmm can make it compatabile with 1.0.0)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Armor has fully physics:&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://imgur.com/gao9dla.gif" width="65%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Guardian had a lot of abilities, that where also applied to any person near it, most of the time the Ancient Hero got these effects&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Head:&lt;br&gt;Stealth Up,&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; Hot Weather Charge&lt;/span&gt;, Cold Weather Charge, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Stormy Weather Charge&lt;/span&gt;, Charge Atk. Stamina Up, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Quick Charge&lt;/span&gt;, Master Sword Beam Up, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Enable Master Sword Beam&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Upper:&lt;br&gt;Stealth Up, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Cold Resistance 2&lt;/span&gt;, Heat Resistance 1, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Impact Proo&lt;/span&gt;f, Hot Weather Attack 2, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Cold Weather Attack 2&lt;/span&gt;, Stormy Weather Attack 2, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Swim Dash Stamina Up&lt;/span&gt;, Unfrezzeable, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Flame Guard 1&lt;/span&gt;, Lightning Proof,&amp;nbsp; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;All Sages wear Masks&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Lower:&lt;br&gt;Stealth Up, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Speed Up 2&lt;/span&gt;, Climbing Speed Up 2, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Snow/Sand Speed Up&lt;/span&gt;, SkyDive Mobility Up 3, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Slip Resistance 2&lt;/span&gt;, Climbing Jump Stamina Up, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Climb Waterfall&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Install Insturctions&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Ryujinx/Yuzu&lt;/span&gt;: Open the zip file and then right click totk and place the romfs in Mod Data Location&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Switch&lt;/span&gt;: Open the zip and search the "romfs" folder and place it in "atmosphere\content\0100F2C0115B6000" on your sdcard&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The armor has alot of Addon Options, just copy the folder/s inside the addon folder you want to use and paste them inside the "romfs" folder, if it asks you to overwrite the files, click "yes"&lt;br&gt;theres no need to recalculate the rstbl if you only added addons.&lt;br&gt;its good for mixing it up with different armors&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://imgur.com/PmcGjaB.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Addon that makes Link Naruto run when the &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Lower&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; is Equiped&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://imgur.com/t72kzsE.gif" width="65%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;I also &lt;b&gt;Plan to add &lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;b&gt;more&lt;/b&gt;, like a Bow and Sword&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Totk Mod manager will release very soon, and it will adding addons like these to your mod more simple&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;Creation:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;This armor was inspired by &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;rt&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Kakashi&lt;/span&gt;, and &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Sheik&lt;/span&gt;. I made it all with Photoshop and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://www.blender.org/download/releases/3-5/" target="_blank"&gt;Blender 3.5&lt;/a&gt;, reusing assets from existing TotK armors, except for the hair, mask, lower sweater, and eye/dye textures.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The hair and mask models were found by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2985366"&gt;General Alciel&lt;/a&gt;. I exported the lower sweater from Roblox using &lt;a href="https://create.roblox.com/landing" target="_blank"&gt;Roblox Studio&lt;/a&gt;, which has some great models that fit the TotK style. The tattoos, called Irezumi, were inspired by some &lt;a href="https://x.com/rinotuna/status/1676528273311035396" target="_blank"&gt;art&lt;/a&gt; I saw.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It took me about &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;four months&lt;/span&gt; to create this armor. I almost scrapped the first design and had some trouble with the physics, which really burned me out. But now, the armor is fully functional. The upper part uses &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Mineru's physics&lt;/span&gt;, and the lower part uses &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Mystic Robe's physics&lt;/span&gt;. I also learned how to add animations to specific armor pieces which is pretty complicated for now with AS edits mostly, but its possible.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I wanted the lower sweater to be part of the upper piece, but I couldn't use Mineru's and Mystic Robe's physics on the same piece. So, I put the sweater on the lower part. This actually turned out better because it allows for cool combos with other armors, though it does cause some &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;clipping with a few pieces&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;The eyes also dont blink&lt;/span&gt;, its not possible to do for now, with armors that fully replace the Head&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I followed an amazing &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/16867"&gt;tutorial&lt;/a&gt; to make the armor standalone, but it doesn’t have a detailed explanation on making it upgradeable yet. I tried to figure that out with some help, but it didn’t work and wasted a lot of time. However, I plan to make it upgradeable in the future.&lt;br&gt;And Never Make 3k+ textures when your armor is dayeable, it will make the game &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;spam&lt;/span&gt; bloodmoons in some areas. The armor also has addons that make Link do a Pose, it uses the Lynel Mask effect, and replacing the animation of the Mask. For the Icons i used&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1782454"&gt;Aster&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/473451"&gt;Armor Icon Helper Tool&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;in the end, its &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; creating this mod unless you get big problems&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Most important thing is to make &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;friends&lt;/span&gt; who will try to help you, and having a strong determination,&lt;br&gt;the &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/nEFVf8A" target="_blank"&gt;Totk Modding Hub Discord&lt;/a&gt; can always try to help&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;You can also always ask me if i have time in Discord "catzy3979"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Disclaimer:&lt;br&gt;Images above where taken while using my other Mod &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/450989"&gt;Sheikah Techniques&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;And &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/480138"&gt;UltraCam&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2745192"&gt;MaxLastBreath&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you want to make video about this mod its fine, if you want to make addons yourself, Please upload only the addon and not the full armor.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/guardian_of_the_goddess_7a5ba.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/guardian_of_the_goddess_no_mask_94745.zip" type="application/zip"/>
