      <guid isPermaLink="false">181615a68b023932ef0d238b17f628a1c1a565bb</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 22:34:21 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6680865ec5f2e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6680873c3b6fe.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6680874735139.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66808752af4f4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/668087590774a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/668087638b283.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6680876ca4b95.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Are you someone who enjoys using a mod that makes fuses invisible... like the &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/449762"&gt;Invisible Fuses&lt;/a&gt; one by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2706240"&gt;Zenovis&lt;/a&gt;? Did you also use the option to restore sheaths, but noticed it did not cover every weapon, &lt;i&gt;and the &lt;/i&gt;offset positions of the sheaths and shields were still just not right?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Well, here's a solution for that!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Simply, I expanded on the original Fused Scabbard Fix... but went ahead and not only added more Swords and Claymores, but made sure the rotation offsets for ALL of them matched their unfused counterparts- including the position of Shield's. A .txt is included in the .7z file that lists all the included and changed weapons, so if there are any you do not want changed, or there is a bug or issue with one, feel free to delete the file or report the problem :)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Also it should be known that &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;mods that alter weapon pack files &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;will not work with this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;... unless you were &lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;to merge them- with say, &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/wips/81203"&gt;TKMM&lt;/a&gt; when it is released&lt;/span&gt; (Join their Discord to stay up to date- they are all legends &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;PLEASE NOTE- IF YOU WANT FUSES TO BE INVISIBLE,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/449762"&gt;DOWNLOAD ZENOVIS'S INVISIBLE FUSES MOD&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;AND &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;USE MY SHEATH RESTORATION WITH IT.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;While I don't use it myself as I prefer the hold position of one handed weapons when fused, the &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/482929"&gt;Normal Sword Hold Position mod&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2828790"&gt;mr.the&lt;/a&gt; will pair great with this for those who want it restored.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I hope you all enjoy &amp;lt;3&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;\/ MODS FEATURED IN SCREENSHOTS \/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/453885"&gt;Invisible Batteries&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;- by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1624188"&gt;MelonSpeedruns&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/449762"&gt;Invisible Fuses&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2706240"&gt;Zenovis&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/523154"&gt;Femme Hero&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2233605"&gt;SpaceGeorge&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/448120"&gt;The Hero's Eyeliner&lt;/a&gt; -&amp;nbsp;by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2233605"&gt;SpaceGeorge&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3 &lt;/span&gt;(Recreated myself for Femme Hero)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/457025"&gt;The Hero's Nail Polish&lt;/a&gt; -&amp;nbsp;by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2233605"&gt;SpaceGeorge&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(Recreated myself for Femme Hero)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/453950"&gt;Hero's Original Arm Restored (Optional Triangle)&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1630162"&gt;Lord Bubbles&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/457509"&gt;Better Wild Set Color&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2785270"&gt;Cool Peas&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(This was broken and relied on an older version- but I fixed it and included it &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/525169"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/456211"&gt;Hero's Weapon's Repaired&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1935258"&gt;Asalazar&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/383076"&gt;Blue-er Master Sword + Hylian Shield&lt;/a&gt; - by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1736451"&gt;iamairhair&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;lt;3&lt;/span&gt; (I only use the Hylian Shield, and edited the dents out to match Hero's Weapon's Repaired)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;/\ MODS FEATURED IN SCREENSHOTS /\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/sheaths_restored_for_invisible_fuses.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
