      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667f9be3bb973.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65867bb3bf2fc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65a7a6d179a78.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65a7a6d1cabad.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/652e10c4cd08c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/650bcc87a263f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64915e5c738b7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/650bcbfb835a3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa415477e0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa435d0aa8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4364938a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa43664bff.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4366bdd2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa43685ce5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4367d54a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa436baea0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa436a0b19.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa436e7f65.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa436eae35.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa436e72ac.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa436f1040.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa436b7a93.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4370a590.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa436f0f92.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa43700395.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa437180ba.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa437204f4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4372560b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4371eff7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4374cf7c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4374d82b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667fa4381df3d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66811eaf2e67a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Very Soon!&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Updates are going well here are some pictures :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Do Not &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Reupload &lt;/span&gt;-&lt;/u&gt; Make outfits for me if you want but don't post my mod inside your mod &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Join my Discord for sneak peaks and stuff just don't flood it with messages lol (Link on my profile)&lt;br&gt;Discord Name: TheRicoLicious ( &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Add Me and ill invite you c:&lt;/span&gt; )&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Leave a Like if you like it lol, Comment or Pm costumes you want separately, and &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;S&lt;/span&gt; &lt;del&gt;U&lt;/del&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt; B&lt;/span&gt; &lt;del&gt;S&lt;/del&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;C&lt;del&gt; &lt;/del&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;del&gt;R&lt;/del&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;I &lt;/span&gt;&lt;del&gt;B&lt;/del&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;E&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;for more! feel free to donate to my PayPal too if you want :) love you Friends&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;These are custom Models/ Textures I made so we can play as my creation Linkette! Her name is Rikuu (Rinkuru). This Beautiful young lady is a Alternate Timeline Heroine who is admired for great or brave acts and courageous qualities. The land of Hyrule remembered her as the hero that fought defeated the evil incarnation of Ganon and erected a statue in her honor in the city of the Zora, the Zora's Domain.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1 data-pm-slice="1 1 []" class="SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;u&gt;NEW:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Animations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;-Running, Jumping, Backstepping, Walking, Fighting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;Hairstyles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;-Default hair, Snowquill Headdress, Diamond, Opal, Amber, Sapphire, Ruby Head Pieces&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;u&gt;This Mod Includes:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;-TRL-Fusions! (Standalone TBA)-TRL-Rico's FlipsNTricks (Edited for Rinkuru)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-TRL-Lightsabers (Standalone TBA)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-TRL-Accessories of Time&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-Shut Up, Link (Made by &lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2656939"&gt;lier90912&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Creator Notes:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;-I Love taking requests  PM me your thoughts and Ideas&lt;br&gt;-Made with v1.1.1,1.2.0 but will work with anything later than 1.0.0&lt;br&gt;-Pronouns She/Her &lt;br&gt;-Voice is in production again for now muted&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Install Instructions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;-Ryujinx: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Place &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;romfs folder&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; in &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;C:\Users\You\AppData\Roaming\Ryujinx\mods\contents\YourModName&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;-Yuzu: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Place &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;entire mod folder&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in C:\Users\YOURNAME\AppData\Roaming\yuzu\load\0100F2C0115B6000\&lt;br&gt;(Or right click your game and select "Open Mod Data Location. Place &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;ENTIRE MOD FOLDER&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; there)&lt;br&gt;It should look like &lt;b&gt;\load\0100F2C0115B6000\&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;ModFolderName&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;\romfs\etc,etc,etc&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;i&gt;-Switch:  &lt;/i&gt;to install, just place romfs into atmosphere\content\0100F2C0115B6000 on your modded switch sd card&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;-RSTB&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Edits for merging or updating:&lt;br&gt;added a rstb.json for merging&lt;br&gt;use mine as a base now there are way to many changes to write out on here and its only gunna get bigger! lol&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Thanks for Everyone that voted in the Poll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</description>
