    <item>
      <title>The Second Quest</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/479009</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">88b63d57a8998f947b45dd13a0822ecacbb582f8</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 11:29:20 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66415e3832340.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6646e2338f909.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6646e233cb3e9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556aa1d3c4f6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65568ee1c1de2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65568b7d4c7bb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f512adc45.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556b66bea8dc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556905c98a47.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556a43c437bc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65539491ce10f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6588ebe49c0f1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f59c82d44.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f59d01b67.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556a262b3208.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556a5730e99c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/656e429b3151f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f5a0543b9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f5a286ac9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f5a014f02.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Translators Needed + Development Progress Update&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hello everyone! We still need translators for &lt;strong&gt;Japanese&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Korean&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;Dutch&lt;/strong&gt;! If you're interested in localizing The Second Quest for one of those languages, please get in contact with YourDiamondDog (yourdiamonddog on Discord) and he can provide the necessary files and information to get started.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We're making steady progress on the 1.1 update, which is primarily focused on polish, balance, and bug fixes. A full change log, spreadsheet, and TSQ combat showcase video are also planned to be released alongside the update.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Also a reminder that TSQ has its own &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://discord.gg/etx2xz6uDR"&gt;Discord Server&lt;/a&gt; for discussion, reporting bugs, and getting more frequent updates on the status of development!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;Rediscover Hyrule Kingdom&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;Tears of the Kingdom: The Second Quest &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;is a large-scale mod being co-developed by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2343073"&gt;deadpanned&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2792161"&gt;YourDiamondDog&lt;/a&gt;, which remixes, rebalances, and reimagines many elements of Tears of the Kingdom to deliver an exciting New Game experience for veteran players or first-time players who favor a modded take on &lt;i&gt;The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom&lt;/i&gt;. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;It is strongly recommended to start a new save file for the best experience!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Features:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overhauled Combat Mechanics faithful to the game's core vision of a versatile physics-based combat system.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rebalanced Weapons and Materials to emphasize real-time tactics and more diverse fusion combinations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Diversified Enemies boasting new properties, greater intelligence, and stronger equipment all across Hyrule.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reworked World Scaling and Economy. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All-New Yiga Schematics and Schema Stones courtesy of &lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/HyruleEngineering/" target="_blank"&gt;The Hyrule Engineering Club&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Remixed Loot, Armor, and Legendary Weapon locations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overhauled Quest Rewards.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;More challenging weather conditions across Hyrule, the Skies, and the Depths, including new underground biomes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overhauled Health Restoration System, further improved from &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/472675"&gt;Cook or Die&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overhauled Armor System, further improved from&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/472574"&gt; Total Armor Rebalance&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional Armor Sets Improvable to raise defense or grant set bonuses.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Updated script including new loading screen tips, tutorial text, and NPC dialogue that matches changes to the mechanics and world. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quality of Life Elements and Unofficial Bug Fixes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Planned Features:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Localization for non-English languages.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Shrine entrances remixed to lead to different shrines.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Improved Schematic Icons.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Improved Cooking System.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional Schematics optimized for 60 FPS compatibility.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mod Customization Options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;...And More!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;Compatibility Info:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Compatible game versions:&lt;b&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.2.0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.2.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have multiple mods that edit these files, use &lt;a href="https://github.com/TKMM-Team"&gt;TKMM (Tears of the Kingdom Mod Manager)&lt;/a&gt; to merge them:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;ResourceSizeTable.Product.&lt;/span&gt;{&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;110&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;121&lt;/span&gt;} file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;RSDB&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Mals&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Tag.Product&lt;/span&gt;.{&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;110&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;121&lt;/span&gt;} file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;GameDataList.Product.110.byml&lt;/span&gt; file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Banc&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Event&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the {&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Actor&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;.pack&lt;/span&gt; files for armor, weapons, food, enemies, Zonai devices, and the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Player.pack&lt;/span&gt; file.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Featured Engineers:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCThhMsHtYHWvd_jri49FInQ" target="_blank"&gt;2CPhoenix&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/BlazeAlchemist991/" target="_blank"&gt;BlazingAlchemist991&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/@chesepuf" target="_blank"&gt;chesepuf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/BlazeAlchemist991/" target="_blank"&gt;Efficienct_Demand5759&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;FantasticPound&lt;br&gt;GoNinjaPro&lt;br&gt;LongJumpingFrame&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/ofstrings2/" target="_blank"&gt;OfStrings2&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ofstrings2" target="_blank"&gt;Wood, Rubber, &amp;amp; Glue&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://on.soundcloud.com/ixGuV" target="_blank"&gt;OshKoshGanache&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Scared_Cry_4931/" target="_blank"&gt;SacredCry&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Shak404/" target="_blank"&gt;Shak404&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Shlowpoke&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtube.com/@ytshotmaker" target="_blank"&gt;Shotmaker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/susannediazz/" target="_blank"&gt;Suusi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://twitter.com/Swapdoodle" target="_blank"&gt;Swapdoodle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Ultrababouin/" target="_blank"&gt;Ultrababouin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
