      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 23:11:50 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667e28f6b09cd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667e292888b94.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667e296440bcd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is my first Tears of the Kingdom mod, so I hope you like it!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod is a simple model-swap of the vanilla Master Sword model to that of the Ocarina of Time model. &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;HUGE thanks to &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1664471"&gt;Tach9&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1935258"&gt;Asalazar&lt;/a&gt;, and the rest of their team, ffor they made the Weapons of Legend mod, and it's from that mod pack that I was able to swap the Master Sword model to it's OoT counterpart.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;and also MASSIVE thanks to the &lt;a href="https://discord.com/invite/cgvw5Cw6Qc" target="_blank"&gt;Tears of the Kingdom Modding Discord server&lt;/a&gt;, for those folks really helped me troubleshoot A LOT of the modding issues I had.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod was made for TOTK Version 1.1.0, and is confirmed to work on a modded Switch. I'm not sure if it'll work for other versions. (See installation instructions for more info)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Extract the .ZIP file, and the copy the romfs folder onto your Totk mod location (e.g. : SWITCH/Atmosphere/Contents/[TOTK ID #]/romfs)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;I would HIGHY RECOMMEND using the &lt;a href="https://github.com/TKMM-Team/Tkmm/releases" target="_blank"&gt;Tears of the Kingdom Mod Manager&lt;/a&gt; or the &lt;a href="https://github.com/MasterBubbles/restbl/releases/tag/1.4.1" target="_blank"&gt;RSTB Calculator&lt;/a&gt; to generate a resource table for your specific version AND to combine multiple mods together.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
