      <title>Challenge Mode Standalone Pack - Lynel Weapons</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/494687</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">81736c33b42dfa2a7148908f924c018d3ac72989</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:25:27 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56c1f78f07.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56aa9cc085.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56ad331c19.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56acda9789.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56b2e37716.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56b54750da.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56b79836df.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56b7e6da1a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56b8444916.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56bd12b790.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56bdb03b34.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65c56be0f08c0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; TSQ compatibility patch fix&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The TSQ compatibility patch is fixed now. The old patch had a small issue that broke the Game Data List and messed with both mods. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;To ensure no more bugs will happen, i made the patch work in a slightly different way. When using TKMM to merge both mods, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;PLACE THE PATCH &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;ABOVE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; LYNEL WEAPONS AND THE SECOND QUEST, THE SECOND QUEST MUST BE RIGHT BELOW LYNEL WEAPONS TO MAKE THE PATCH WORK.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed The Second Quest Compatibility issues.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;A small port of one of the many features TOTK &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/projects/36566"&gt;Challenge Mode&lt;/a&gt; mod will have, the return of Lynel Weapons. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Each of the weapons have a new set effect made for them, the Shield Weapon.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/478039"&gt;True Damage Display&lt;/a&gt; mod was included as a built-in feature and now all Lynel Weapons are also part of the Compendium.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;All Lynels in the game now use Lynel weapons based on their tier with scaling enable as well. I highly suggest you to play this mod with &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/479009"&gt;The Second Quest&lt;/a&gt; mod made by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2343073"&gt;Deadpanned&lt;/a&gt; &amp; &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2792161"&gt;YourDiamondDog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;PLEASE USE ONLY THE COMPATIBILITY PATCH WITH TKMM TO MERGE THE MOD WITH TSQ, THE MOD ITSELF HAS SOME FEATURES THAT CAN MESS WITH TSQ IF NOT HANDLED PROPERLY.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;PLACE THE COMPATIBILITY PATCH ABOVE LYNEL WEAPONS AND SECOND QUEST MOD ON TKMM TO ENSURE NO BUGS WILL HAPPEN BETWEEN BOTH MODS.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Enjoy.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
