    <item>
      <title>Mystic Headpiece Replacements</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/523994</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">3c77cd8adbbfec3bb88652e32c63664d98cc2a9c</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 05:54:21 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667bac39d9b68.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667bac39c5990.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667bac5cc22c9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667bd12425e83.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/667e400f57950.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacements&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Replace the &lt;b&gt;Mystic Headpiece&lt;/b&gt; with one of the following:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacement - Fire&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ember Headdress head piece with Mystic Headpiece hair&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacement - Frost&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Frostbite Headdress head piece with Mystic Headpiece hair&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacement - Lightning&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Charged Headdress head piece with Mystic Headpiece hair&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacement - Lynel&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Horns from Lynel mask with Mystic Headpiece hair/headband&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacement - Phantom Horns (&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;NEW&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Horns from Phantom helmet with Mystic Headpiece hair/headband&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacement - Light Dragon (&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;NEW&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Light Dragon horns with Mystic Headpiece hair/headband&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;I liked the headpieces of each of the elemental headdresses and wanted to combine it with the Mystic Headpiece hairstyle. Originally wanted to replace each of the elemental headdresses but couldn't figure out how to replace them and keep the Mystic Headpiece hair animations etc. If you know how to do this, let me know (or feel free to try yourself).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Installation instructions&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ryujinx&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unzip and pick a version and copy/place mod folder (&lt;code&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacement - Fire&lt;/code&gt;) into mod directory e.g. &lt;code&gt;C:\Users\YOURNAME\AppData\Roaming\Ryujinx\mods\contents\0100f2c0115b6000&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;If you are using other mods, make sure to run &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tools/15857"&gt;RESTBL Calculator&lt;/a&gt; to merge rsizetable changes for all mods&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Yuzu&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unzip and pick a version and copy/place mod folder (&lt;code&gt;Mystic Headpiece Replacement - Fire&lt;/code&gt;) into mod directory e.g. &lt;code&gt;C:\Users\YOURNAME\AppData\Roaming\yuzu\load\0100F2C0115B6000\&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;If you are using other mods, make sure to run &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tools/15857"&gt;RESTBL Calculator&lt;/a&gt; to merge rsizetable changes for all mods&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
